Fig. 2 A-D
). Paratype : INV EQU4234, one specimen, total length 35 mm; collected in El Faro rocky reef, Cabo Marzo, northern Choco , Colombia ( 6°49.4802'N , 77°41.3976'W ), by M.J. Vanegas, 24 April 2016; at 13 m depth under rocks and attached; GenBank nucleotide sequences 16S MK477992 ( Fig. 2E ); Paratype : INV EQU4312, one specimen, total length 25 mm; collected in Morromico rocky reef, Gulf of Tribuga , northern Choco , Colombia ( 5°52.3194'N , 77°18.6426'W ), by G. Borrero, 20 Oct 2016; at 10 m depth under rocks; GenBank nucleotide sequences COIMK477998 ( Fig. 2F ).

